    message: '‚ö†Ô∏è No handling issues were connected!

To use this workflow:
1. Look at the issue nodes (blue üîµ for understeer, red üî¥ for oversteer)
2. Connect the nodes that match your car's behavior to the "Collect Issues" merge node
